        <p>Hi, I&rsquo;m Lucana — short-form content strategist and video editor. Since 2023, I&rsquo;ve been helping brands turn views into something that actually matters: enrollments, attendance, sales.</p>
        <p>I don&rsquo;t just edit. Before I touch a timeline, I define who the video is for, what they need to hear, and what we want them to do next. Then I write the script. Then I cut it. That full-system approach is how two videos I produced for an education academy reached <span class="hl">400K+ views</span> — with 150+ comments asking how to enroll. It&rsquo;s also how a single campaign video put <span class="hl">100+ people in the room</span> at a live event for a tech institute, pulling nearly 200K views and 19K likes along the way.</p>
        <p>Most of my work has been with education brands, but the method travels: wherever there&rsquo;s a story to tell and a customer to win. Based in Bolivia, working US hours.</p>
